headline: ZBH Q1 Earnings Call: Revenue Tops Expectations, Guidance Lowered Amid Tariff and Integration Headwinds
summary: Medical device company Zimmer Biomet (NYSE:ZBH) reported Q1 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 1.1% year on year to $1.91 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.81 per share was 2.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
